title: Ethereum Up or Down on April 18?
description:

This market will resolve to "Down" if the "Close" price for the Binance 1 minute candle for ETHUSDT 17 Apr '25 12:00 in the ET timezone (noon) is higher than the final "Close" price for the 18 Apr '25 12:00 ET candle.

The resolution source for this market is Binance, specifically the ETHUSDT "Close" prices currently available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/ETH_USDT with “1m” and “Candles” selected on the top bar.

Please note that this market is about the price according to Binance ETHUSDT, not according to other sources or spot markets.

title: ECB Interest Rates: June 2025

title: Will Russia capture Siversk by August 31?
